title: Set of Rational Numbers
text: The set of rational numbers includes fractions written as $$\frac{m}{n}$$ where m and n are itnegers, and n does not equal 0.

title: Set of Irrational Numbers
text: The set of irrational numbers is the set of numbers that are not rational, are nonrepeating, and are nonterminating

title: Square Roots of Prime Numbers
text: The square root of a prime number is always irrational.
